@startuml activity_receive_and_reconcile_goods
title Activity Diagram - ReceiveAndReconcileGoods

start
:Warehouse Department receives physical delivery of goods;
:System loads expected order quantities from Overseas Order;
:Unpack and count received merchandise;
:Compare actual received quantity with expected ordered quantity;
if (Is there a discrepancy?) then (yes)
  :Record discrepancy (surplus/deficit/damaged);
else (no)
  :Mark as fully matched;
endif
:Save Goods Receipt details;
:Update internal warehouse stock levels;
stop
@enduml
